  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is provided each morning with freshly baked pastries, local jams and hot options including eggs, bacon and sausages. </p>
<p>Dinner is a choice of four courses. The restaurant is full of character with a decorative mix of vintage paintings, quirky statues and trinkets. You can enjoy fresh fish dishes and platefuls of pasta. The food is great quality and freshly made using local ingredients. There's also a fantastic wine list to go with it!</p>
<p>The bar service opens up onto the terrace and gardens throughout the day - it's a great place to watch the sunset.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
