  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are about 20m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed) and have a view of the square, some rooms may also have a glimpse of the lake, but this is not guaranteed. Please request double or twin beds at the time of booking (triple rooms are available on request).</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Rooms</strong> are about 25m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a balcony overlooking the lake.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Rooms for sole use</strong> are also available.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Bath with showerhead</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request, free of charge.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of approx. €1.50 per person per night is payable locally, applies to guests age 14 and over.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
